## PolyForm Perimeter 1.0.0 Restriction (addendum)

<https://polyformproject.org/licenses/perimeter/1.0.0>

As an addendum to the PolyForm Small Business License above,
you may not use the software to provide a service whose
primary purpose overlaps with the capabilities provided by
the software itself. Specifically, you may not offer a
compliance-as-a-service, travel-rule-as-a-service, or
